    "long_instructions": "## Interior Design\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out ideas for decorating a room.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Look at the images already uploaded to this level and decide if you'd like to use those or images of a room more relevant to you.\r\n2. Decide on new areas you'd like to come up with ideas for. Here are some common topics:\r\n\t- Furniture & Layout\r\n    - Lighting\r\n    - Color & Walls\r\n    - Texture & Fabrics\r\n    - Decor & Accessories\r\n    - Technology & Smart Features\r\n    - You can use AI chat to help you brainstorm more ideas if you'd like!\r\n3. Add the images you want to include in your input to your prompt.\r\n4. **Adjust** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n>Help me brainstorm ideas around **[insert area of interest here]** in this room.\r\n5. Press **Send**.\r\n6. **Change and add to your prompt** to see if you can get AI Chat to provide you more useful responses.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-picture-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload a file I found?**]\r\n- Download the file (image or PDF) on to your device\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Device**\r\n- Then locate the file on your device.\r\n- When you find the file to upload, select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::",
